Product description

Why Choose LightingWill's 2Inch 5W Smart Lighting?

  • High Quality: The smart recessed lighting is crafted with precision using aluminum alloy and flame-retardant PC materials, ensuring a sleek and elegant design. It boasts exceptional quality and strong durability.
  • DIY Group Management: Customize your lighting experience by grouping the recessed lighting according to different areas or preferences. This feature allows for personalized lighting setups tailored to your needs.
  • Smooth Dimming: Enjoy the unique 1%-100% smooth dimming feature of the smart lights. It enables precise adjustment of light intensity, creating the most comfortable lighting effects for every moment.
  • Music and Lighting Integration: With a built-in music player and 8 scene sound effects, this smart cabinet light seamlessly integrates music with lighting. It offers a one-touch activation for a whole new sensory experience.
  • Long-lasting Durability: With a lifespan of up to 50,000 hours, this 2 inch led recessed lighting ensures stability and reliability. It provides enduring lighting protection, allowing you to enjoy the comfort of smart lighting.

Unleash Your Daily Palette

With our smart led recessed lighting, you have the freedom to choose the color temperature for your day: integrating RGB and CCT dual-color temperature design, adjustable from 2700K to 6500K.

Whether you desire the warm glow of golden hues or the refreshing coolness of blue tones, our light can meet the demands of various scenes.

Explore a myriad of possibilities, tailor the perfect ambiance for every moment, and infuse your world with vibrant colors!

LigtingWill Smart WIFI LED Recessed Lighting Dimmble

Specification:

  • Power: 5W
  • Input Voltage: 90-265V AC
  • Color Temperature: RGB & CCT 2700K-6500K Color Changing
  • Dimmable: Dimmable
  • Brightness: 350LM
  • Material Type: Aluminum + Flame Retardant PC
  • Front Diameter: 70mm/2.75inch
  • Cutout Opening Diamerter: 53mm/2.08 inch
  • Height: 34.8mm/1.37 inch
  • Life Span: 50000 hours

Package Includes:

4 X 5W Dimmable Smart LED Downlight

Note:

  • Only compatible with 2.4GHz network, 5GHz network is not supported.
  • The light can only be dimmed by App & voice control, not compatible with the DIMMER switch.


Voice Control

Control your smart lighting via your voice with Alexa, Google Assistant and so on. Just give a voice command to turn on/off or dim/brighten your smart Downlight, even switch your WIFI downlight to specific olor as you need.


Remote Control

Remote control smart downlight with your phone through Smart Life, Smart Life App no matter where you are. You can control the WIFI LED bulb individually or create different groups to control the lights.


Devices Sharing

Families can share the smart colorful life together via the smart bulb with intimate families. Sharing device and sharing your care for intimate families at the the same time.
